title: BREAKING: Three people knifed in Hollywood stabbing spree
text:
BREAKING: Three people knifed in Hollywood stabbing spree BREAKING: Three people knifed in Hollywood stabbing spree AT LEAST three people have been stabbed in an attack in Hollywood. PUBLISHED: 22:38,  42, Tue, Jan 31, 2017 TWITTER At least three people have been stabbed in an attack in Hollywood 
The attacker reportedly went on a stabbing spree on Sunset Boulevard. 
Local media say it is unclear how many people were knifed. 
The surrounding area has been put on lockdown and police called to the scene. 
It is unclear how serious the victims injuries are. 
CNN says the attacker has been shot by police.
